# ViperSQL — An in-memory SQL database engine
project sqldb
version 0.1.0
lang zia
entry main.zia

# === Package Metadata ===
package-name ViperSQL
package-description "An in-memory SQL database with full query support"
package-identifier org.viper-lang.sqldb

# === Assets ===
asset docs docs
asset README.md .

# === File Associations ===
